Stalonetray is a STAnd-aLONE system TRAY (notification area) for X
Window System. It has full XEMBED support and minimal dependencies:
the X11 lib only. Stalonetray works with virtually any EWMH-compliant
window manager.

After install, copy /etc/stalonetrayrc to to ~/.stalonetrayrc to make
per-user settings changes.
